<!-- these scripts can get moved to a .js file prior to going live. -->

<script type='text/javascript'>
<!--
// jump to page header when page loads, effectively hides the location bar and gives more room for content 'above the fold'.
// if #noMastHead is set, jump down to below the search

window.addEventListener("load", function() { setTimeout(loaded, 100) }, false);  
function loaded() { 
	document.getElementById("page_wrapper").style.visibility = "visible";   
	
	if(location.href.indexOf('#noMastHead') > 0)	{
		window.scrollTo(0, 93);
		}
	else	{
		window.scrollTo(0, 1); // pan to the bottom, hides the location bar   
		}
//	alert(window.orientation);
	}
// -->
</script>
